{"tid":2478794,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"補牙問題","createTime":"2021-04-07T10:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T17:28:43.000Z","uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6be5848c8628e1aaa2399ee3bfcd9338f679cd74","tid":2478794,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:21:58.000Z","msg":"我12月到3月補左三次牙了<br />\n因為補牙材料一係甩出黎 一係食野果陣碎左<br />\n依家第三次用銀粉補 暫時仲健在<br />\n我想問點解唔用其他更硬嘅材料補嘅？ 鈦金屬得唔得呀"},{"pid":"8eb7204887e553d4cad5b7b84611a3ac3700e8d4","tid":2478794,"uid":304264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:11:26.000Z","msg":"補牙通常一係用銀粉一係用樹脂 冇得用鈦金屬架 因為冇得痴實隻牙<br />\n銀粉最堅固架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa630851a9f2d7819cbc52117618a2c5cf2f84e","tid":2478794,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:12:35.000Z","msg":"個窿要夠大先可以用其他材料"},{"pid":"59497ca07fe24bfb8852b4ab1eaf730e5dc25125","tid":2478794,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8eb7204887e553d4cad5b7b84611a3ac3700e8d4","tid":2478794,"uid":304264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:11:26.000Z","msg":"補牙通常一係用銀粉一係用樹脂 冇得用鈦金屬架 因為冇得痴實隻牙<br />\n銀粉最堅固架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T17:14:47.000Z","msg":"可唔可以底果層用銀粉, 只有表面果一層用樹脂, 咁咪又有堅固, 又睇唔出囉, 就算咬爛樹脂, 都仲有下面銀粉完整無缺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4eb61cdde3b2d6b64caf0f369da41637042fa4","tid":2478794,"uid":36339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T17:17:09.000Z","msg":"我都補完不過唔知用咩物質補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢話1年內甩左免費搞"},{"pid":"92baa4072a667af3aa38888d97cf6f1adf5e99a0","tid":2478794,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T17:18:33.000Z","msg":"究竟人間之中有咩物料揀"},{"pid":"ad194a13046c1f8d205dbc53b157d2a05dfd3547","tid":2478794,"uid":213295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T17:20:09.000Z","msg":"鑲金牙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a02b52859e5862cd0a667c8c86fdddbbf49059","tid":2478794,"uid":221089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T17:28:43.000Z","msg":"如果剝咗智慧齒之後有冇得用黎磨做牙粉補其他牙呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（都係用佢啲膠水痴返落去啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"}]}